{"title": "The law needs more bite against people who abuse or abandon animals", "tags": "opinion", "timestamp": "2024-02-26", "content": "When it comes to animal cruelty, I feel an intense need to say something.\nAnimal cruelty and abandonment cases reached an 11-year high when the Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Animals (SPCA) detailed a 79 per cent increase in reported cases in its 2023 annual report. It investigated more than 900 cases in 2023."}